{"tid":2238011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［共享中國人的榮光］［直線抽擊中共］一人一信寄去MP，要求取消胡鍚進兒子的加藉","createTime":"2020-10-10T18:01:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T01:33:36.000Z","uid":380266,"like":160,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"f43c176cf321fde283e02e151634c677b8b0d4db","tid":2238011,"uid":380266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T18:01:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我係來自加拿大的連登仔，我整咗封信俾大家去信加拿大國會，胡錫進身為共產黨成員，在2019香港反修例示威中，他曾敦促香港警察槍擊示威者。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進為了利益不斷打壓香港民主運動。不斷抹黑示威人士。一個不尊重人權，民主的人，他的下一代又怎可以生活在一個資本主義及尊重人權、民主、開放的西方國家？而且胡本人對西方國家極不友善。所以不應該接受一個容易破壞普世價值的人移民加拿大。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他的兒子來到加拿大會危害加拿大國家安全。我僅此要求禠奪其兒子加國護照及重發權利！<br />\n<br />\n中英文可能都唔係幾好，請大家多多海涵。<br />\n<br />\n信：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/15HGJ4fvfa5praZTNEtGvKgh4PIju8Z4ANQ8kLjq_Dl0/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F15HGJ4fvfa5praZTNEtGvKgh4PIju8Z4ANQ8kLjq_Dl0%2Fedit&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlUBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=aef62e88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/15HGJ4fvfa5praZTNEtGvKgh4PIju8Z4ANQ8kLjq_Dl0/edit</a>"},{"pid":"fe396fdeb35053087e7ebbf580e393ea0c1aafd2","tid":2238011,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T18:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5286c2caff5a3af32ddf77bc4edbdf9e4d4e4203","tid":2238011,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T18:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm